<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
           .header-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 300px;
            background-image: url('https://www.akshayapatra.org/includefiles/userfiles/images/disater-relief-feeding.jpg'); /* Replace with your image URL */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .caption {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #FF0080;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -40px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 80%;
        }
    .container {
            width: 60%;
            margin: 80px auto 0;
            padding: 40px;
            background-image: url('your-background-image-url-here.jpg'); /* Replace with your background image URL */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: black;
            background-color: white; /* Background color for better text readability */
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px #00FF80; /* Margin color effect */
        }
        .heading {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #00FF80;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .section h2 {
            color: #FF0080;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .contact-bar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background-color: #2E8B57;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .contact-bar div {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .contact-bar button {
            background-color: #FF0080;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1em;
        }
        .contact-bar button:hover {
            background-color: #ff3399;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header-image">
        <div class="caption">"Together, we restore hope and rebuild lives, proving that love and compassion can conquer adversity."</div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="heading">Vision</h2>
            <p>Our vision is to create a compassionate world where every individual affected by natural disasters receives timely support and assistance. We aim to foster resilience in communities, empowering them to rebuild their lives and restore their dignity in the aftermath of calamities.</p> </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="heading">Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to mobilize resources and raise awareness to support victims of natural disasters. We work tirelessly to provide essential aid, including food, shelter, and medical assistance, to those in need. Through community engagement and partnerships, we strive to ensure that no one faces the challenges of disaster recovery alone, offering hope and rebuilding lives together.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-bar">
        <div>
            <h3>Address</h3>
            <p>123 Helping hands Lane, Heritage City, India</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3>Email</h3>
            <p>contact@helpinghands.com</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3>Contact Us</h3>
            <button>Get in Touch</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>